title: Autonomicon  Icarus Messerschmitt  2017
description:
Autonomicon - is an international Belarussian-Polish band.The group was founded in 2004. The group's music is a mixture of weird, neurotic, disturbing and sad ballads, resembling some deconstructed Velvet Underground songs, combined with the sound effects, which may remind of the Japanese minimal, ambient and glitch. Musicians rarely play on stage and mostly for very small audiences.  Most of the songs are available to free download.

2017 new album was recorded in Vietnam, Poland, Germany and Belarus and had good reviews in russian/belarus experimental music related media
